{"tid":433360,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[高汁劣改] 《肥閪》原:《天網》","createTime":"2017-10-12T10:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T07:43:43.000Z","uid":153493,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"666cb5783303ceeb8c6c3a71595ba542bd0d90c2","tid":433360,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"肥婆是一生孤獨 大腸爆了無忘吃肉<br />\n總可以狂吃 不打算要郁 滿身肥肉<br />\n肥柒沒一點不毒 被恥笑也仍愛燒肉 <br />\n美極唔甜美 d屎會變宿 何時滿喜屋<br />\n<br />\n肥人心裏想痛哭 何人懂我極狂妄<br />\n明明無做錯 仍愛嘲諷 我今受重傷<br />\n誰人知我極難過 仍然堅信心裏所愛<br />\n人人唾罵我 仍要不怕失望 力威卻沒法幫我<br />\n<br />\n情願是一起孤獨 並非你女神們多慾<br />\n請相信羅莽 頂撚到佢穿 臭閪淫蕩<br />\n如何令脂肪轉贈 贈歡笑你們去煮熟<br />\n外在無完美 心中卻滿足 神明會祝福<br />\n<br />\n而如今再不痛哭 何妨跟你再直往<br />\n傻人向後看 仍困昔往 那需要重傷 <br />\n(炸雞伴美酒)<br />\n肥神知你心所思 仍然堅信心裏所愛<br />\n無誰愛護您  何要周處張望 你便靠你一雙手"},{"pid":"3f955e3bc519e71b19e2d42430da40b4eb863142","tid":433360,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"小弟肥柒毒不才<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開完ac即開埋post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔岩音改得柒咪見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求屌細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a23302923e5fc5d5f3c2dac3159a07ba56398cb","tid":433360,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"玩下十連先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=